                <%= link_to "Wednesday evening bible study, 6:30 p.m." , "#{@evening_bible.url}" %>
              </strong> No class on Ash Wednesday. We begin a new series on March 9, examining the culture in the time
              of Jesus. Join us in person in the library or through the internet.</strong></p>
            <p><strong>
                <%= link_to "Thursday wine time, 5:30 p.m." , "#{@wine.url}" %>
              </strong> This is a popular and relaxing chat room open to everyone who wishes to join in. Usually
              called "Thursday wine time," <strong>it's on Friday </strong> when the vestry meets, usually on the
              third Thursday of the month.</p>
            <p><strong>Join us for coffee </strong> after the Sunday morning worship service. It's a time for
              fellowship and to meet new friends. Parishioners bring snacks to share, and there's always plenty for
              everyone.</p>
            <%= link_to cl_image_tag("#{@pathway.image}", width: "99%" ), "#{@pathway.link}" %>
              <p><strong>New Pathways available </strong> Click on the image above to read or download the latest
                edition (<%= @pathway.pubdate.strftime("%B %Y") %>) of <em>Pathways,</em> the parish newsletter.</p>
